YAMPDC - Yet Another Music Player Daemon Client

YAMPDC is a music player daemon client written in Ruby. It runs in the 
background with a system tray icon. Playback control can be done by 
right-clicking on the icon. Left-clicking on the systray icon will bring up the 
main window. From this window, song information can be seen and playback can be 
controlled, as well as a progress bar will show.

DEPENDS:

Gems: 
	gtk2
	librmpd => librmpd.rubyforge.org

Usage: 
	Use ruby to execute yampdc.rb.
